    IMapTileProviderCallback

    public class OfflineTileProvider
extends MapTileProviderArray
implements IMapTileProviderCallback
    Causes Osmdroid to load from tiles from only the referenced file sources and no where else. online sources are not even attempted.
    Since:
    5.0 Created by alex on 6/14/2015.
